---
title: Creamy Mushroom Fettuccine with Sun-Dried Tomatoes
description: Nothing says comfort and indulgence like a rich creamy pasta! From the earthy sauteed thyme mushrooms to the tang of the sundried tomatoes, these flavours are carried through in the lush sour cream sauce. Wilted spinach and reserved pasta water help lighten this soon to be dinner classic.
